As a user
I want buttons and vote count on the side of each post
So I can up-vote and down-vote each post while also seeing how many net up-votes each post has.

As a user
I want a search bar displayed on each page of the website 
So I can search for posts and get appropriate search results based off of my input

As a user
I want a dropdown list of hyperlinks to popular subreddits
So I can view the list and be redirected to a given subreddit when clicked

As a user 
I want a “my subbreddits” bar 
So I can easily view all of the subreddits which I am subscribed to
